Gimtteoksun mereka sangat enak.

106
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,160
Maaf, apa?

107
00:06:04,629 --> 00:06:06,829
Gimtteoksun, gimbap, tteokbokki, dan sundae.

108
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,529
Kamu mau membelikannya untukku sekarang?

109
